Bai 4 Hero layout and Form

Muc dich la de tao ra mot layout va form cho dung chuan

vao bulma -> documentation -> layout -> hero

Chon trong do cai Fullheight title
sau do xoa het <body> </body> di
Copy phan Fullheight title vao va se thay ket qua

Xoa het phan nay di

<h1 class="title">
Fullheight title
</h1>
<h2 class="subtitle">
Fullheight subtitle
</h2>

Thay the bang cai nay

<div class="hero-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns is-centered">
      <div class="column">
      Xin moi login  
      </div>     
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

Se thay ket qua
Muon no co nho lai thi them cai nay vao nua
<div class="column is-6-tablet is-6-desktop is-6-widescreen">
  
Bay gio them anh vao thi cho cai nay vao
<div class="columns is-centered">
<div class="column is-6-tablet is-6-desktop is-6-widescreen">
<div class="field has-text-centered">
<img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/598192263626301440/BwPMAyDK_400x400.jpg">
</div>

De tao form login ta vao documentation -> form -> general
copy phan login vao trong do

muon sua nut login ta sua lai thanh
<button class="button is-danger is-fullwidth">\

muon them bat cu cai gi cung phai cho vao <div class="field">

vao form -> select se gap duoc mot dropdown
de them mot o check box chung ta them cai nay
<label for="" class="checkbox">
<input type="checkbox"> Remember Me

bai 5 button and icon

vao documentation -> elements -> button
xuong phia duoi co cai with font awesomeicons

copy doan nay vao phia ben duoi

<button class="button is-primary">
<span class="icon">
<i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
</span>
<span>Twitter</span>
</button>

khi them is-fullwidth vao cuoi button is-primary thanh button is-primary is-fullwidth
cai nut Twitter se bi keo dai ra

vao trang fontawesome.com